HEADWORD: Colloquialize
<hw>Col*lo"qui*al*ize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To make
colloquial and familiar; <as>as, to <ex>colloquialize</ex> one's style
of writing</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

